verbose_text: As shown in XREF_FIG, the L-4, IL-10 and IL-13 protein levels were significantly increased when the islets were co-cultured with either ADMSCs or ADMSCs-BET; the IL-4 levels in the ADMSCs-BET group were significantly higher compared with those in the ADMSCs group (all P < 0.05).
